column5: Hi,  I will be canoeing on Lady E and Temag lakes in about a month. Does anyone know where to find paper copies of depth maps for these 2 lakes? I checked Anglers Atlas and Fish-ON w/o sucess. Thx
Google will be your best bet.

Adventure fishing maps... they come laminated. http://www.adventurefishingmaps.on.ca/ You'll need two for Temagami.. same deal for Lady E depending on your plans. $9.95 each. Also probably available at "Gramps" Outdoor store at Angus lake, but I'd call first.. or get you order in direct to adventure now.
Thx, guys. Looks really good---I'll check them out.
PM me your email if you want the PDF versions.  They are likely better quality.

Thx, FL. I was able to download PDFs for Lady E. I tried searching on that site for Lake Temag but didn't find. I didn't see how to narrow my search to just look amongst maps, or browse to find other maps. Looks like quite a useful site, though----thx for providing that link
